name: Eddie Vedder, Pearl Jam, Barcelona, November 1996
description: Eddie loved to climb PA’s. It always looked death defying, and there was always that element of danger involved - would he jump or not? And if he did, would he break his neck? Those thoughts and worries were especially strong with the crew. This was the No Code tour - when I look at this picture I can still hear the call and response of “Ole, Ole, Ole, Ole!” Charles Peterson
